HEADWORD: dart board
<hw>dart board</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a
circular board of wood or cork used as the target in the game of darts.
It may have any of several patterns on it, such as concentric circles,
or a central circle with rays.</def>⟦br⟧
